{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Tp1pScg4NDZ4D3tgBHHz97","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→def is_prime(n: int) -> bool:\n     2→    \"\"\"n が素数かどうかを返す。\n     3→\n     4→    Args:\n     5→        n: 判定する整数\n     6→\n     7→    Returns:\n     8→        素数なら True\n     9→    \"\"\"\n    10→    if n < 2:\n    11→        return False\n    12→    if n < 4:\n    13→        return True\n    14→    if n % 2 == 0 or n % 3 == 0:\n    15→        return False\n    16→    i = 5\n    17→    while i * i <= n:\n    18→        if n % i == 0 or n % (i + 2) == 0:\n    19→            return False\n    20→        i += 6\n    21→    return True\n    22→\n    23→\n    24→def primes_up_to(n: int) -> list[int]:\n    25→    \"\"\"n 以下の素数一覧を返す（エラトステネスの篩）。\n    26→\n    27→    Args:\n    28→        n: 上限値\n    29→\n    30→    Returns:\n    31→        n 以下の素数のリスト（昇順）\n    32→    \"\"\"\n    33→    if n < 2:\n    34→        return []\n    35→    sieve = [True] * (n + 1)\n    36→    sieve[0] = False\n    37→    sieve[1] = False\n    38→    for i in range(2, int(n**0.5) + 1):\n    39→        if sieve[i]:\n    40→            for j in range(i * i, n + 1, i):\n    41→                sieve[j] = False\n    42→    return [i for i, v in enumerate(sieve) if v]\n    43→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"310d8377-ec71-462e-9ae9-44ad9400a6fa","uuid":"a1e18409-d7af-494e-8e7a-d70e14f4037b","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/nao/work/sefirot/src/toy/prime.py","content":"def is_prime(n: int) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"n が素数かどうかを返す。\n\n    Args:\n        n: 判定する整数\n\n    Returns:\n        素数なら True\n    \"\"\"\n    if n < 2:\n        return False\n    if n < 4:\n        return True\n    if n % 2 == 0 or n % 3 == 0:\n        return False\n    i = 5\n    while i * i <= n:\n        if n % i == 0 or n % (i + 2) == 0:\n            return False\n        i += 6\n    return True\n\n\ndef primes_up_to(n: int) -> list[int]:\n    \"\"\"n 以下の素数一覧を返す（エラトステネスの篩）。\n\n    Args:\n        n: 上限値\n\n    Returns:\n        n 以下の素数のリスト（昇順）\n    \"\"\"\n    if n < 2:\n        return []\n    sieve = [True] * (n + 1)\n    sieve[0] = False\n    sieve[1] = False\n    for i in range(2, int(n**0.5) + 1):\n        if sieve[i]:\n            for j in range(i * i, n + 1, i):\n                sieve[j] = False\n    return [i for i, v in enumerate(sieve) if v]\n","numLines":43,"startLine":1,"totalLines":43}}}
